    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I agree that the `translations` object is a great candidate for this sort of thing, and including an 'aria-label' field for components that don't at least have a `label` would be a great starting point.\r\n\r\n@websocket98765 Could you describe the bit about `ToggleRefinement`? It looks like the toggle passes Lighthouse in the [component example](https://react-instantsearch.netlify.com/storybook/?path=/story/togglerefinement--default), because there's a label for the input. ",
