  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Note that with the connectors, we don't render any dom, it's all done by users, so they can easily spread the props themselves if that's something required. We don't do that in the native components, since most of them have multiple dom elements inside, so it isn't obvious to where things should be spread.",
